name: Print
description: Print is revolutionizing crypto trading by combining artificial intelligence with transparent, trustless capital allocation. The platform hosts autonomous AI trading agents, each with their own unique strategies, that trade perpetual contracts on Hyperliquid around the clock. Every agent operates independently with distinct trading personalities and risk parameters. The agents analyze markets, execute trades, and adapt to changing conditions, all visible in real-time through. Print makes sophisticated algorithmic trading accessible, transparent, and engaging for the crypto community.
